sky.f1.uk.description: The F1 Academy field line up on the grid for the first of three races this weekend at Circuit Gilles-Villeneuve. Chloe Chambers begins P1 based on the final grid from Miami race two.

sky.f1.uk.title: Canadian F1 Academy: Race 2
sky.f1.uk.description: The F1 Academy field line up on the grid for the second race of three this weekend in Montreal. Britain's Chloe Chong occupies reverse-grid pole after finishing eighth in qualifying.

sky.f1.uk.title: Canadian F1 Academy: Race 3
sky.f1.uk.description: The all-female F1 Academy field line up on the grid for the third and final race in Montreal. American Chloe Chambers leads the way after out qualifying her teammate on Friday.

sky.f1.uk.title: Canadian F1 GP: Qualifying
sky.f1.uk.description: The grid for the Canadian Grand Prix is set with F1 qualifying at Circuit Gilles-Villeneuve in Montreal, as the drivers look to battle their way through to Q3 for a shot at pole. (14.06)

sky.f1.uk.title: Ted's Quali Notebook

sky.f1.uk.title: Lando Norris's Career

sky.f1.uk.title: Grand Prix Sunday: Canada

sky.f1.uk.title: Canadian F1 Grand Prix

BloombergTVEurope.uk.title: Bloomberg Tech
BloombergTVEurope.uk.description: The only daily live technology program with a focus on breaking news, market-moving reporting and analysis of global technology companies and stories.

BloombergTVEurope.uk.title: Bloomberg Markets
BloombergTVEurope.uk.description: Bloomberg Markets is focused on bringing you the most important global business and breaking markets news and information as it happens.

BloombergTVEurope.uk.description: Kevin Hassett, National Economic Council Director discusses the negative impact of the recent government shutdown on GDP and the administration's strong legal standing on tariffs. S11, Ep7

BloombergTVEurope.uk.description: AT&T CFO Pascal Desroches has partnered with CEO John Stankey to restructure the company around a core of fibre and 5G wireless connectivity. S5, Ep3

BloombergTVEurope.uk.title: Bloomberg Businessweek Daily
BloombergTVEurope.uk.description: Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec bring you reporting from the magazine that helps global leaders stay ahead, plus insight on the people, companies and trends shaping today's complex economy.

BloombergTVEurope.uk.description: Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld break down the day's top market-moving stories and trading action around the closing bell.

BloombergTVEurope.uk.description: Bloomberg Balance of Power focuses on politics and policies on Capitol Hill, in President Trump's administration, the federal agencies and the courts.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Halloween II: Peralta and Holt repeat their Halloween wager, as Peralta bets the Captain that he can steal his watch before midnight. (S2 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Natural Born Kissers: Homer and Marge spice up their love life by snuggling in public places, including a barn and the crazy golf course. But then they lose their clothes... (S9 Ep25/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: My Mother the Carjacker: Homer's long-lost mother (guest star Glenn Close) arranges to meet him. But after she's apprehended by police, Homer must free her from a prison bus. (S15 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Old friends return to lift Donny's spirits. And it's a race against time as a revenge plot closes in on one resident.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Once Upon a Time in Springfield: Krusty gets a beautiful new co-star (guest voice Anne Hathaway). Mr Burns withdraws the staff's free doughnuts at the nuclear power plant. (S21 Ep10/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Inside the World's Most...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Luxurious Cruises: A look behind the scenes aboard some of the world's most opulent cruise ships, where suites cost up to 8k a night and pets are as pampered as their people. (S1 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch The Gentlemen, Casualty, Who Wants to Be a Millionaire?, Crufts, Queens, and Martin Compston's Norwegian Fling. (S23 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch The Great Celebrity Bake Off for SU2C, Hunted, One Day, Anton & Giovanni's Adventures in Spain, Married at First Sight Australia and more. (S23 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Open House: The Great Sex...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Experiment: Chelsea and George seek a threesome, but will it help Chelsea move past George's sexually adventurous past and infidelity? Jess and Ben host a naked dinner party. (S2 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: After dating a few love rats, beautician Gemma wants to find her Prince Charming. Tattoo artist Jennafer is fed up with men and is looking for the perfect woman. (S2 Ep4/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch The Gentlemen, Casualty, Who Wants to Be a Millionaire?, Crufts, Queens, and Martin Compston's Norwegian Fling. (S23 Ep5) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers watch The Great Celebrity Bake Off for SU2C, Hunted, One Day, Anton & Giovanni's Adventures in Spain, Married at First Sight Australia and more. (S23 Ep6) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Inside the World's Most...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Luxurious Cruises: A look behind the scenes aboard some of the world's most opulent cruise ships, where suites cost up to 8k a night and pets are as pampered as their people. (S1 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Muscles Mirsky: When Beverly is caught out reading Erica's diary she promises to trust her daughter instead of snooping in future, but Erica takes advantage. (S1 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Goldbergs Never Say Die!: Adam and his friends go on a treasure hunt inspired by comedy adventure film The Goonies when Pops misplaces some family jewels. (S1 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Don't Tell the Bride
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sofia dreams of a boho beach blessing, but Craig wants an Oktoberfest wedding with short leather trousers. Will Sofia end the nuptials?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Year of Birthdays: As the birth of Haley and Dylan's twins approaches, the family look back at how each of them celebrated their birthdays this past year. (S10 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Catch of the Day: Phil is convinced he's going to have a bad luck day after failing to complete his daily superstition. Mitch is certain that Cam is undermining him. (S9 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: A short, cheeky clip featuring animals and food, from the always hilarious Tube that is Rude.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Junior Bake Off
E4Plus1.uk.description: It's halfway through Finals Week and the bakers create the ultimate sharable party food, before they take on a supersized Showstopper. Who'll go big, and who'll go home? (S11 Ep13/15) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Capri: In Eagle Rock, California, Gordon helps Capri, a restaurant in a rut that's owned by identical twins Jim and Jeff and is closed more often than it's open. (S4 Ep12) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Christmas Story: Beverly tries to breathe new life into the family's holiday traditions by launching a new celebration: Super Hanukkah. (S3 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Tasty Boys: Adam and Barry form a rap super-group just like the Beastie Boys. Beverly fights for her right to redesign the kitchen. (S3 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Double-Click: Claire can't seem to find the right time to fire an employee, Phil thinks he caught Luke with a girl in his bed, and no one notices that Alex has moved back. (S7 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Tale of Three Cities: There's a reunion after trips took the Dunphys to New York; Mitch, Cam and Lily to the Midwest; and Jay, Gloria, Manny and Joe to Juarez in Mexico. (S8 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Leone's: Rose built her Italian restaurant in New Jersey into a thriving business, but when she spent two years in hospital, her son ran it into the ground. Can Gordon save it? (S5 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Burger Kitchen (Part 1/2): In the first half of a two-part Nightmare, Gordon tries to save a burger joint in LA, run by a dysfunctional family in a state of constant conflict. (S5 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Full Boyle: Boyle's new romance increases his self-confidence, Diaz and Santiago can't take a costumed crime-fighter seriously, and Holt faces a leadership challenge. (S1 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Apartment: Peralta is in danger of losing his flat but has no money to buy his own place, so Gina tries to help him find a new home. The officers do self-evaluations. (S1 Ep18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Lisa the Simpson: Lisa starts to suspect that she's not as clever as she used to be and worries that she'll end up a permanent underachiever like her father. (S9 Ep17/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: This Little Wiggy: Bart is invited to the Wiggum household and finds it filled with police equipment: a troublemaker's paradise. (S9 Ep18/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dungeons & Dragons, Anyone?: Adam picks a team of popular athletes over his friends in gym class. Erica decides that she wants to leave home to go to college. (S3 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Rush: When Barry insists that Beverly always favours Adam, she tries to make amends. Murray's not happy about Erica's new boyfriend, a fanatical music fan. (S3 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ringmaster Keifth: Cam tries to make up for his Thanksgiving debacle by hosting a New Year feast. And Phil's not sure how to feel about his dad dating his childhood babysitter. (S8 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sarge & Pea: Cam is incensed when a rude parent robs him of a precious Lily moment during her dance recital. Jay, Claire and Mitch unexpectedly run into Dede at a family wedding. (S8 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Mole: When an Internal Affairs investigator reveals that there's a mole in the precinct, Peralta and Holt must find out who it is before Wuntch catches on. (S2 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Jake and Sophia: Peralta hits it off with a woman in a bar, only to find out that she's the defence attorney representing a suspect who he wants to put in jail. (S2 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The President Wore Pearls: Principal Skinner cancels sport, art and music at the school to save cash, so the students - and the police - go on strike. With Michael Moore. (S15 Ep3/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Regina Monologues: The Simpsons go to London with $1000 that Bart found, but Homer crashes the hire car into the Queen and gets locked in the Tower. Tony Blair guest stars. (S15 Ep4/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Treehouse of Horror Presents Simpsons Wicked This Way Comes: A mysterious tattoo-covered fella at the carnival tells Lisa three surreal stories. (S36 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Million Dollar Maybe: Homer wins the lottery jackpot but has to keep it secret from the family. Guest starring Chris Martin from Coldplay. (S21 Ep11/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Britain's Most Expensive Houses
E4Plus1.uk.description: The show that takes a lavish peek into extraordinary properties. Broker Josh digs deep into his network to close a deal on an 80 million penthouse in Knightsbridge. (S3 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Britain's sharpest armchair critics watch The Apprentice, Hunted, Corrie, The Underdog: Josh Must Win, Bridge of Lies, and the News on the Princess of Wales' cancer diagnosis. (S23 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Goggleboxers tune in to Gladiators, Is It Cake?, Casualty, The 1% Club, The Yorkshire Farm, This Morning, BBC News on the cost of living, and more. (S23 Ep8)

Film4.uk.title: The Contractor
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Action thriller with Chris Pine. An ex-soldier takes on private work to feed his family, but finds himself in dire straits (danger; not the band). With Kiefer Sutherland.

Film4.uk.title: Commando
Film4.uk.description: (1985) Thriller starring Arnold Schwarzenegger. To free his kidnapped daughter, an ex US commando must agree to assassinate a South American president. But he's not as pliant as he seems...

Film4.uk.title: Les Misrables
Film4.uk.description: (2019) Ladj Ly's oscar-nominated drama, loosely based on his childhood and set in the struggling Parisian suburbs of Montfermeil during the 2018 riots. In French/subs.

Film4.uk.title: Siege at Red River
Film4.uk.description: (1954) Western. Van Johnson stars as a Confederate agent who steals a Gatling gun prototype from the Yankees and attempts to smuggle it south through enemy lines to his own side.

Film4.uk.title: Mary, Queen of Scots
Film4.uk.description: (1971) Vanessa Redgrave stars in a dramatisation of the life of the 16th-century Scottish queen. Glenda Jackson co-stars as her cousin and rival, England's Queen Elizabeth I. Violence.

Film4.uk.title: Robin and Marian
Film4.uk.description: (1976) Touching romance starring Sean Connery and Audrey Hepburn. The ageing legend Robin Hood returns to Sherwood Forest and discovers that, while he was away, Marian has become an Abbess.

Film4.uk.title: The Enemy Below
Film4.uk.description: (1957) Second World War thriller. Robert Mitchum stars as the captain of a US destroyer in the North Atlantic hunting down a German U-boat and its world-weary captain, Curt Jurgens.

Film4.uk.title: Titanic
Film4.uk.description: (1997) Leonardo DiCaprio and Kate Winslet star in James Cameron's Oscar-winning epic. Lovers from across the social divide meet on the doomed luxury liner.

Film4.uk.title: The Crying Game
Film4.uk.description: (1992) Stephen Rea plays an ex-IRA terrorist who's pursued by a deadly assassin, Miranda Richardson, to London, where a love affair complicates matters. Very strong language/violence.

Film4.uk.title: The Principles of Lust
Film4.uk.description: (2003) Drama starring Alec Newman. A man must choose between his stable relationship and his thrill-seeking friends. Strong violence/very strong language/graphic sex/drugs.

Film4.uk.description: Teleshopping.

Film4.uk.title: Man in the Saddle
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Western. Randolph Scott stars as a rancher who's the target of unwelcome harassment by his richer and more powerful neighbour. With Alexander Knox, Joan Leslie and Ellen Drew.

Film4.uk.title: This Gun for Hire
Film4.uk.description: (1942) Classic noir starring Alan Ladd and Veronica Lake. As a cold-blooded assassin seek vengeance for a double cross, he unwisely falls for the girlfriend of the cop who's pursuing him.

Film4.uk.title: Anzio
Film4.uk.description: (1968) Epic Second World War drama starring Robert Mitchum. A reporter gets trapped behind enemy lines during the costly 1944 Allied invasion of Italy. With Peter Falk and Robert Ryan.

Film4.uk.title: Gunman's Walk
Film4.uk.description: (1958) Western. Van Heflin stars as a veteran frontiersman whose determination to mould his sons in his gun-totin' image backfires disastrously. With Tab Hunter and James Darren.

Film4.uk.title: Fighting with my Family...
Film4.uk.description: ...Interview Special: Florence Pugh, Jack Lowden, Nick Frost and director Stephen Merchant discuss making the comedy-drama that's based on a real-life family of wrestlers from Norwich.

Film4.uk.title: The Eagle
Film4.uk.description: (2010) Historical adventure with Channing Tatum and Jamie Bell. A Roman commander and his British slave embark on a risky mission to recover a military mascot lost in Scotland.

Film4.uk.title: Polite Society
Film4.uk.description: (2023) Nida Manzoor's kick-ass martial-arts anti-romcom stars Priya Kansara as a college student and wannabe stuntwoman who wants to save her older sister from an undesirable marriage.

Film4.uk.title: xXx
Film4.uk.description: (2002) Action thriller starring Vin Diesel as Xander Cage: a thrill-seeking extreme sports enthusiast, stuntman and rebellious athlete-turned-reluctant spy. With Samuel L Jackson.

Film4.uk.title: xXx: The Next Level
Film4.uk.description: (2005) Action thriller sequel with Samuel L Jackson, Ice Cube and Willem Dafoe. There's a new Triple X agent in town and he's up against some shady government business.

Film4.uk.title: The Sheriff of Fractured Jaw
Film4.uk.description: (1959) Comedy western with Kenneth More. An English gunsmith decides the Wild West is the best market for his wares, but little does he expect to end up sheriff of a lawless frontier town.

Film4.uk.title: The Desert Fox
Film4.uk.description: (1951) Drama. James Mason stars in Henry Hathaway's sympathetic portrait of Field Marshal Erwin Rommel in the final years of his life during the Second World War. With Jessica Tandy.

Film4.uk.title: Tobruk
Film4.uk.description: (1967) World War II thriller. George Peppard, Rock Hudson and Nigel Green lead a daring Allied raid to destroy Nazi fuel dumps in North Africa.

Film4.uk.description: (2017) Fantasy adventure starring Matt Damon and Willem Dafoe. In 11th-century China, Europeans seeking the secret of gunpowder are caught up in a war against alien monsters.

Film4.uk.title: The Last of the Mohicans

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Rover SD1/Jag 240: Derek collects a Mark 2 Jag and explains why they made such poor getaway cars for bank robbers. A customer considers a Morris Marina as a present for his wife. S1 Ep7

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: AC Cobra/Volvo F8T8: The team have a record number of cars to auction, but Derek finds room for one more - a replica AC Cobra. A couple are reunited with their Volvo breakdown truck. S1 Ep8

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Abandoned Engineering
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Ghosts of the Swamp: Forgotten relics from the defence of America's homeland, concealed by the banks of the Mississippi, and a concrete behemoth on the French coast that proved invulnerable. S5 Ep6

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: The Ratline: The hunt for Adolf Eichmann, who arranged the transportation of millions of Jewish people to death camps, and Nazi secret police chief Klaus Barbie. S4 Ep2

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Shopping from Home.

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Great British Railway Journeys
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Urmston to New Islington: Michael Portillo is in Greater Manchester, hearing about the birth of the NHS and the first episode of Coronation Street. S14 Ep2

UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.title: Bangers & Cash
UAndYesterdayPlus1.uk.description: Rolls Silver Shadow/Austin 7: A widow reluctantly parts with her husband's treasured collection of Rolls Royces and Bentleys, and an impulse buyer finds one of the cars a new home. S1 Ep10
